summary:
I am a native french and native English speaker born in London.I grew up in Marseilles in the south of France.

I currently live in the Netherlands and work as sales consultant for Sungevity .Before that i worked as a contractor for Hewlett & Packard, a sales manager for a company specialised in extrication tools the previous year and as an account manager in the optical retail business.
Prior to those positions I was an account manager for the internet hotel booking reservation site Easytobook.com for 18 months and before that, for the same length, for their main competitor the market leader Booking.com as a customer service representative .

In those positions, I greatly improved my overall sales processes (acquisition, sourcing, logistic, marketing, affiliates marketing and direct sales). l also sharpened at the time my knowledge of the tourism and travel sector in both B2B and B2C relations while setting up the sales campaigns for my customers. 

Being a native English and French speaker at ease with figures and invoicing, support, logistics and communication, I am also pro active as well as a team player .I am persistent and make it my pride to reach the goals given.I have a deep sens of empathy and i am assertive in my approach to work when defining and fulfilling my customers needs. I have a high exigency towards my work rate and strong daily sharpened communication skills.
